  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Switzerland by Train 2024/2025</h2>
<p><span>Get on board and experience Switzerland by train. </span><span>With room to stretch and views to wow, your holiday starts the moment you step aboard.</span></p>
<div class="c-tabs-beta__content-table--row-wrapper">
<p><img src="/media/13100456/lake-lucerne-weggis-2.jpg" alt="switzerland by train" data-udi="umb://media/5438b0f54e3d4f308d069d1f6bbe040e" /></p>
<h3>Switzerland Holidays by Rail</h3>
<p>Enjoy stunning views, comfort and hassle-free travel long before your boots hit the trails. Sit back, relax, and stretch out.</p>
<p>Ready to experience Switzerland by rail? Book online by selecting 'London St Pancras' for departure or <a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">contact us</a> to find out more.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">All Aboard For Luxury: FREE First Class Rail Upgrade</h3>
<p>Book a walking holiday with us and enjoy a complimentary first-class upgrade on your rail transfer to and from your Switzerland resort. Sit back, soak up the views and let us treat you to an unforgettable journey. <a href="#terms" data-anchor="#terms">*T&amp;C's apply</a>.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea}?&amp;from=QQS" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="?&amp;from=QQS">View Switzerland Holiday Deals</a></p>
