<h3>All Aboard For Luxury: FREE First Class Rail Upgrade</h3>
<p>Book a walking holiday with us and enjoy a complimentary first-class upgrade on your rail transfer to and from the airport to your Switzerland resort. Sit back, soak up the views and let us treat you to an unforgettable journey. *T&amp;C's apply.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea}?&amp;from=QQS" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="?&amp;from=QQS">View Switzerland Holiday Deals</a></p>
<p id="terms" style="text-align: left;"><strong>*Swiss Rail Upgrade Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Buy a Swiss holiday with Inghams Walking and receive a free upgrade to First Class on your rail transfer from to/from resort.​</span></li>
<li>Applicable on holidays to Switzerland only.​</li>
<li>Valid on all departure dates between May 2024 and September 2024 and May 2025 and September 2025.​</li>
<li>The upgrade will automatically be added to the booking during the booking process.​</li>
<li>The offer is not applicable on all rail travel to and from the UK.​</li>
<li>Offer applies to new bookings only​</li>
<li>This offer is subject to availability and can be withdrawn or amended at any time without notice</li>
</ul>
